productBaseInfoV1.title: Fenix UC35 LED Spot Light
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The Fenix UC35 rechargeable flashlight combines the best features of all Fenix-models in one high-quality torch. This makes it a very interesting Fenix torch. The UC35 can provide an output of 960 lumens for 1 hours and 30 minutes. But it also has an eco-mode with an output of 14 lumens. In this eco-mode, the torch provides 150 hours of light. When the battery runs out, you can easily charge it with the USB-cable that is included in delivery. The connection for this cable is protected by a rubber cap. We recommend to press the cap well after charging, to secure the protection. You control all modes, using the switch on the side of the torch. This switch also functions as an indicator while charging. When the switch is red, the torch is still charging. It turns green once the charging process is complete. Do remember to switch on the tactical switch at the back of the torch, in order to start the charging process.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Fenix UC45 LED Spot Light
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: This rechargeable torch by Fenix offers you the comfortable feeling you always have a fully charged torch within reach. The torch is powered by a USB-cable. That means you can find a suitable power supply everywhere. Both a computer and adapters can be found everywhere. And it can also be charged in the car. Where many torches powered by a USB-cable have a rubber cap to protect the connection, the UC45 has a ring just behind the head of the torch that has to be unscrewed. When the charging is completed, you refasten the ring and the solid and waterproof protection is ensured again. In addition to the USB-connection, an LED shows if the torch is being charged (red) or if the charging process is completed (green).4 different light settings can be selected ranging from 10 to 960 lumens. This means a modest amount of light in the low position, ideal to be able to lighten something nearby and an enormous light bundle in the highest position with a reach of 257 m.The torch is operated by 2 buttons. You switch the torch on or off using the switch at the back of the torch. You select the several light settings using the position switch. The stroboscope position can be selected immediately by keeping the ?selector switch? pressed. This also works if the torch is not burning yet.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Victorinox Rally Red Swiss Army Knife(Red)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The Victorinox Rally Red Swiss Army Knife is a popular, small and light weight multi-purpose knife that is made to exacting standards with dozens of steps going into its construction. It is a compact multi-tool kit for on- the-spot use. Victorinox attends to every detail, from selecting the finest materials to performing the final inspection. The Victorinox Rally Red Swiss Army Knife is a perfectly sized pocket knife, which is very convenient to carry around and consists of the basic tools that can be used around the house for precarious tasks or can be useful when you are out trekking, mountaineering or camping. It is truly a versatile multi-functional knife designed for specific tasks. Body and Features The Victorinox Rally Red Swiss Army Knife is part of the original Swiss Army Knives Collection. The Rally is stylishly cased in a classic red housing with the iconic Victorinox logo on the side. The designer accessory weighs just 22 g and the small size allows the accessory to discreetly fit in your pocket if you are out on an adventurous trip. This Rally Red Swiss Army Knife contains 9 handy main tools; in addition to the blade the tool features tweezers, tooth pick, key ring, screwdriver, nail filer, scissors and bottle opener. These utilitarian set of tools is held together in place with the help of a brass rivet and the metals parts are fastened to this rivet with Brass flanged bushings. The separators between the tools are made from aluminium alloy and are constructed in a manner to resist corrosion or scratches from the adjacent tool. The standard cutting blades are made out of premium quality stainless steel and are handy around the house and on weekend excursions. The blades and other parts feature small fingernail slits to make drawing out the parts easier. The tweezers that is a part of the knife is a tool used for picking up objects too small to be handled with your fingers. If you carry this handy knife with you on an outing you need not carry an extra key ring or key chain for your keys to the car, bike or house; you can secure all the keys in the metal key ring that is fastened on one end of the knife. There are 3 kinds of screwdrivers accommodated in this multi-tool knife; small screw driver, large screw driver and Phillips screw driver, which can be used to drive screws and bolts and sometimes for rotating other machine elements. The other function of the small and large screw driver parts is to open cans and bottles, respectively. Hence, you need not spend on an extra set of can and bottle openers. The knife comes with a unique tool, a nail filer, which is handy for women on the go or you can use it to smoothen a sharp edge. This classic Swiss Army knife also features a toothpick; it was originally made for the soldiers out in the field. This Rally Red Swiss Army knife is affordable, works well and provides good value. Precision quality and functionality are the hallmarks of any Victorinox Swiss Army Knife.
